Here is the implementation of the poll(int) method for the KafkaProducerService class:

``java
public Optional<SpaceCollector> poll(int partition) {
    // Get the next message from the Kafka topic.
    ProducerRecord<String, Object> record = kafkaTemplate.poll(topicName, partition);

    // If there is no message, return an empty Optional.
    if (record == null) {
        return Optional.empty();
    }

    // Convert the message to a SpaceCollector object.
    SpaceCollector spaceCollector = (SpaceCollector) record.value();

    // Return the SpaceCollector object.
    return Optional.of(spaceCollector);
}
`